# CX_DB8 Help & Models Recording
# Run with: vhs demo_help.tape

Output assets/help_v2.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "uv run cx-db8 --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "uv run cx-db8 models"
Enter
Sleep 4s
